<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.7">
<l>miṉṉotta nuṇṇiṭaiyāy meyyaṭiyēṉ viṇṇappam</l>
<l>poṉṉotta māṉoṉṟu pukuntiṉitu viḷaiyāṭa</l>
<l>niṉṉaṉpiṉ vaḻiniṉṟu cilaipiṭittem pirāṉeka</l>
<l>piṉṉēyaṅ kilakkumaṇaṉ pirintatumō raṭaiyāḷam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lady with the lightening thin waist!</l>
<l rend="indent">I am your true servant, Salutations!</l>
<l>When the golden deer entered [the forest] and played sweetly,</l>
<l>in accordance with your wishes,</l>
<l rend="indent">our Lord grasped [his] bow and left,</l>
<l>and Lakṣmaṇa departed after [him].</l>
<l>This is one proof.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
